title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 17 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 17 2022
description:
Charles Gasparino of Fox Business joins Clay and Buck to talk Wall Street, Biden and inflation. BLM Founder caught paying millions to family and friends. Coward Chuck Schumer declines debate with Tucker Carlson after writing Rupert Murdoch a letter calling him racist. Jordan Peterson under fire for SI Swimsuit issue tweets. PA Primary Day with C&B: Kathy Barnette joins C&B with her closing argument.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
